{"tid":2236052,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"玩物達人●上妝植髮 figure reborn  眼神殺死人 頭雕戲味濃","createTime":"2020-10-09T07:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T07:43:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6084cab7e7e9883ad365d9f7e58a3c12564bdc37","tid":2236052,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/tech/20201009/OIDSV3RW7VE2NKLY33Y6POU3UM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ftech%2F20201009%2FOIDSV3RW7VE2NKLY33Y6POU3UM%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=0f419c4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ftech%2F20201009%2FOIDSV3RW7VE2NKLY33Y6POU3UM%2F&h=f2722a24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/tech/20201009/OIDSV3RW7VE2NKLY33Y6POU3UM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n玩物達人●上妝植髮 figure reborn <br />\n眼神殺死人 頭雕戲味濃<br />\n<br />\n香港玩1:6 figure的人很多，大部份都愛收藏大廠出品，但對大廠頭雕不滿的亦為數不少。雖然諸多不滿，但願意為頭雕重新上色的又有幾多人？千多二千元的心頭好，又有幾多人放心讓外人重新改裝？<br />\n<br />\n郭子明（Aaron）本身愛看電影，10年前買了一款《搏擊會》figure散件自組，由於不滿頭雕質素，遂到坊間找人重新塗裝。機緣巧合下，發現有一間玩具店貼出塗裝一個頭雕收費600元的告示，上堂學塗裝也只收600元，Aaron自覺太挑剔，恐怕別人的手工未必可滿足他，所以最後決定報名學習塗裝，就此展開了塗裝頭雕的生涯。他最初將自己的成品上載到網上分享，吸引網友查詢問價，就這樣開始了為客人訂做塗裝頭雕的兼職，至今已重塗了數百個作品。他的客人來自世界各地，。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nAaron認為，「一個出色的figure頭雕，就是能展露出角色神髓，否則，就是浪費了這件作品。」因此，他不會隨意接單，「我會看看頭雕的原型，想像若重新塗裝後，會讓角色的神似度提升多少，若能做出明顯的提升，我就會接單，若效果差別不大，我就會向客人解釋。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pg2mZVWUA8ctAEKLFEEQRc4VRkc=/5174x2920/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CFBMGVYUYBGYFF5JLHMCV44B24.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fpg2mZVWUA8ctAEKLFEEQRc4VRkc%3D%2F5174x2920%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCFBMGVYUYBGYFF5JLHMCV44B24.JPG&h=f773dbc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAaron會替客人重新塗裝figure頭雕，一般千多元起。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nJ9h2-YNsVc60TcQ-uqU973af1w=/3936x2624/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JNBHCLQBWJBR5HXSCS7FLPRFMM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnJ9h2-YNsVc60TcQ-uqU973af1w%3D%2F3936x2624%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJNBHCLQBWJBR5HXSCS7FLPRFMM.JPG&h=0ded003c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要為頭雕植上頭髮，要先將原本的塑膠頭髮（左起）鏟走，將頭雕變成光頭狀態後才能植髮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/m8KZtAShhFxtGHV4hF0PKDLOytU=/5184x2920/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Z4LHDO2VZ5GPVI3EEMVKGNI4GY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fm8KZtAShhFxtGHV4hF0PKDLOytU%3D%2F5184x2920%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZ4LHDO2VZ5GPVI3EEMVKGNI4GY.JPG&h=292015af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n收集了數百個figure的Echo，是Aaron的長期顧客，已找他塗裝了十多個頭雕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眼眉五層色 用羊毛植髮<br />\n<br />\n現在的頭雕技術進步了，皮膚紋理也能呈現，不少頭雕在白模件時已非常神似，他認為一般只要肯將頭雕重新塗裝，會比廠方上色有一定層次上的提升，「只要你把頭雕交給我，我就會全神貫注地處理，不同於廠商以大量人手的生產線大批大批製造，當然是訂做塗裝能將神髓大幅提升，即使是同一個頭雕仍會看得出很大分別。」以Hot Toys為例，官方圖片上頭雕原型樣辦會由一個主力塗裝師上色，大家都以照片上作品的質素決定是否預訂，「但貨品推出後因為並非由該名塗裝師操刀，貨品往往與樣辦有出入。」<br />\n<br />\n收到客人的頭雕後，Aaron會先將原本的顏色洗掉，然後噴灰，再觀察有沒有瑕疵要補，補灰後就會直接上色。「先是皮膚，接着是眼睛，之後會再仔細處理層次感。一般膚色塗裝，外國人角色的話約三層，底色、陰影和紋理，細節的處理如眉毛等大約四至五層；至於眼睛，瞳孔和周邊的放射線和光亮油等約三至四層。」。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F4_rf4XWPaYSSRNvjJUM1BoiBJ0=/5184x2920/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ANI5FIIJLFBRPHC5MHJ4CVXVRM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF4_rf4XWPaYSSRNvjJUM1BoiBJ0%3D%2F5184x2920%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FANI5FIIJLFBRPHC5MHJ4CVXVRM.JPG&h=98793dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《鎗王》哥哥以Enterbay的寧采臣頭雕改裝，凸顯憂鬱神情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qzSjNBEIlT5qqTJ-NpHvOikwfrQ=/3936x2624/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KD5ME6TZJNGHFMRV3LLHNCRYD4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqzSjNBEIlT5qqTJ-NpHvOikwfrQ%3D%2F3936x2624%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKD5ME6TZJNGHFMRV3LLHNCRYD4.JPG&h=ff6402f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因喜歡美劇《絕命毒師》，Aaron自購頭雕和散件改裝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gmmvdovUGe1WFH6S4-X6WUG3gYs=/3936x2624/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KUHA2K6O5RBPLN7KXL2KVEINHU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgmmvdovUGe1WFH6S4-X6WUG3gYs%3D%2F3936x2624%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKUHA2K6O5RBPLN7KXL2KVEINHU.JPG&h=04c25f0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小丑在植髮和再上色後，更凸顯電影角色的詭異神髓。<br />\n<br />\n《雷霆救兵》的湯漢斯figure，是Aaron為客人Echo重塗的首款作品。<br />\n《雷霆救兵》的湯漢斯figure，是Aaron為客人Echo重塗的首款作品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DrXzcFfbmqfcr5XfyDGltI3kt14=/3936x2624/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SYLBCUV23RGNZH24XF4WVRGXZ4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDrXzcFfbmqfcr5XfyDGltI3kt14%3D%2F3936x2624%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSYLBCUV23RGNZH24XF4WVRGXZ4.JPG&h=ecb7ce74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n較少人喜歡的Marvel英雄鷹眼，也有客人找Aaron重塗和植髮，令鷹眼看來更帥氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鎗王哥哥 「表現戲中失控情緒」<br />\n<br />\n一般來說，客戶等一至兩個月就可以取回完成品，但現時需時或會較長，因Aaron手頭上有不少客人的頭雕正在排隊，其中光顧了多次的老顧客Echo更與他成為朋友。Echo幾年來找Aaron塗裝了十多款figure，大部份都是電影角色，「他第一個幫我塗裝的是電影《雷霆救兵》的湯漢斯，效果出色，非常有電影感。其實大廠出品也很仔細，但膚色和神情總是做不好，尤其是眼神。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yKZcXrqf1ZT69QM0y_j9f4OO3IY=/3936x2624/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FJPDIG6MVZGIJFC7KUFT7O7UP4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyKZcXrqf1ZT69QM0y_j9f4OO3IY%3D%2F3936x2624%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFJPDIG6MVZGIJFC7KUFT7O7UP4.JPG&h=37599a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAfter：水行俠經重新塗裝和植髮，真實感大幅提升。<br />\n<br />\nBefore<br />\nBefore<br />\n<br />\nAfter：除了重新塗裝和植髮，寧采臣figure的衣服和道具都做了舊化效果。<br />\nAfter：除了重新塗裝和植髮，寧采臣figure的衣服和道具都做了舊化效果。<br />\n<br />\nBefore<br />\nBefore<br />\n<br />\nAfter：John Wick在Aaron加工後，更顯角色的落泊和堅毅。<br />\nAfter：John Wick在Aaron加工後，更顯角色的落泊和堅毅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_S3kuQlsdSw0uLbwASBlQDYE-HA=/1286x1242/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TQXGQB5WVNAU7KR2A5BH6BHYIU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_S3kuQlsdSw0uLbwASBlQDYE-HA%3D%2F1286x1242%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTQXGQB5WVNAU7KR2A5BH6BHYIU.jpg&h=1f847f07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBefore<br />\n<br />\nAfter：Echo最喜歡《希魔撞正殺人狂》軍官的塗裝頭雕。<br />\nAfter：Echo最喜歡《希魔撞正殺人狂》軍官的塗裝頭雕。<br />\n<br />\nBefore<br />\nBefore<br />\n<br />\n記者：馬子聰<br />\n<br />\n攝影：張志孟、鄭明川"}]}